Decrypt an encrypted RDS file

ezyr_decrypt_rds.Rd

Decrypt an encrypted RDS file

Usage

ezyr_decrypt_rds(filepath, key = NULL)

Arguments

filepath

(character) File path to RDS file

key

(character) Optional argument for ask_for_key, which will be called internally. Defaults to NULL, for which the user will be prompted for a passkey at runtime via rstudioapi::askForPassword

Value

Decrypted RDS file

Examples

# ezyr_decrypt_rds("C:/Users/<your_username>/.../your_encrypted_file.rds")
